    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the <strong>chicken</strong> has browned, transfer it to a plate for later, reserve the pan</p><p>Add the <strong>onion wedges, sliced</strong> <strong>pepper </strong>and<strong> chopped garlic</strong> to the reserved pan and cook for 4-5 min or until starting to soften</p>",
