    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once softened, add the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong>, <strong>basil stalks </strong>(you'll use the leaves later!), <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> and <strong>dried oregano</strong> to the pan</p><p>Add in your <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>stock mix</strong> and season with a good grind of <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Cook for a further 2 min, stirring regularly</p>",
